{
  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What is IRAP?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  The Industrial Research Assistance Program (IRAP) is Canada's largest\n                  and most established technology assistance program for small and medium-sized\n                  enterprises. Administered by the National Research Council of Canada (NRC),\n                  IRAP has supported Canadian innovation for over 75 years.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  IRAP provides <strong>non-repayable contributions</strong> (grants) to help\n                  fund R&D projects, along with free access to technical and business\n                  advisory services. Unlike SR&ED tax credits that reimburse after spending,\n                  IRAP provides upfront funding to accelerate innovation.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Advantage:</strong> IRAP funding is 100% non-repayable and\n                    provides upfront capital—you receive payments as you complete project\n                    milestones, not after filing taxes. This cash flow advantage is critical\n                    for R&D-intensive SMEs.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for IRAP Funding?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                IRAP eligibility centers on company size, Canadian incorporation, and\n                innovation focus. The program specifically targets growth-oriented SMEs\n                with technology development mandates.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Eligible Companies\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>SME status</strong> – 500 or fewer full-time employees</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Canadian incorporated</strong> – active Canadian operation</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>For-profit</strong> – commercially oriented business</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Innovation focus</strong> – R&D or technology mandate</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Growth potential</strong> – capacity to commercialize</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Not Eligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Large corporations (500+ employees)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Non-profit organizations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Universities and research institutions</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Government entities</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Companies without technical innovation</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"mt-6 bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> IRAP considers \"potential for growth\" heavily.\n                  Even early-stage startups with strong technology and market potential can\n                  qualify. The key is demonstrating commercial viability of your innovation.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Much Funding Can You Get from IRAP?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                IRAP funding varies based on project scope, company size, and regional\n                priorities. The program typically funds 50-67% of eligible project costs.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-green-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Funding Element</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Details</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Maximum Grant</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600 font-bold\">Up to $1,000,000</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Typical Range</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">$50,000 – $500,000</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Cost Share</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Up to 67% of eligible costs</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Repayment</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600 font-bold\">None – 100% Non-Repayable</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Youth Employment</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Up to $40K/year (75% of salary)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Stacking</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Can combine with SR&ED claims</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Important:</strong> Average IRAP project funding is approximately\n                  $320,000. Larger projects over $500K require additional review and\n                  stronger justification.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Project Costs Does IRAP Cover?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                IRAP primarily funds salaries and wages for technical personnel, with\n                limited coverage for contractors and materials. Understanding eligible\n                costs is critical for accurate budgeting.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center text-green-800\">\n                    Eligible Expenses\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Salaries and wages (technical staff)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Contract research services</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Prototype materials and supplies</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Testing and validation costs</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>IP protection (limited)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Subcontractor costs</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border border-red-200\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center text-red-800\">\n                    Ineligible Expenses\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Capital equipment (major purchases)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Marketing and sales activities</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>General administrative overhead</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Working capital</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Costs incurred before approval</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Owner/shareholder salaries (limited)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What are the IRAP Funding Streams?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      R&D Project Funding\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-green-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-green-700\">Up to $1M</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Per Project</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-700\">67%</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Cost Coverage</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-700\">12-24 months</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Typical Duration</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                      Core funding for technology innovation, product development, process\n                      improvements, and applied research activities.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Youth Employment Program\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-green-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-green-700\">Up to $80K</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Per Hire</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-700\">75%</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Salary Coverage</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-700\">12-24 months</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Placement</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                      Wage subsidies for hiring recent STEM graduates (within 3 years)\n                      aged 15-30 for innovation-related positions.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Advisory Services\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-green-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-green-700\">Free</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">No Cost</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-700\">200+</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">ITAs Across Canada</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-700\">Ongoing</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Support</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                      Free access to Industrial Technology Advisors (ITAs) providing\n                      technical guidance, business mentorship, and network connections.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Do You Apply for IRAP Funding?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Contact Your Local ITA (1-2 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Reach out to an Industrial Technology Advisor in your region. ITAs\n                      are your first point of contact and guide you through the entire\n                      process. Find your local ITA on the NRC website.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Initial Assessment (2-4 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Your ITA evaluates your company's eligibility, innovation\n                      capacity, and growth potential. This includes reviewing your\n                      technology, team, and commercialization strategy.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Project Development (2-6 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Work with your ITA to define project scope, technical milestones,\n                      timeline, and budget. Your ITA provides guidance on what makes a\n                      strong project proposal.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Proposal Submission</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Submit your complete project proposal through your ITA. The proposal\n                      includes technical plan, budget breakdown, commercialization\n                      strategy, and milestone schedule.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">5</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">NRC Review (4-8 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      NRC evaluates technical merit, commercial potential, and project\n                      feasibility. You may be asked for clarifications or additional\n                      documentation during review.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">6</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Contribution Agreement & Execution</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Upon approval, sign the contribution agreement and begin project\n                      execution. You receive payments as you complete milestones and\n                      submit claims.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Documents Are Required for IRAP?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Company Documentation\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Articles of Incorporation</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Financial statements (2-3 years)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business plan</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Organization chart</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Key personnel resumes</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Project Documentation\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Technical project description</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Detailed budget breakdown</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Milestone schedule</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Commercialization strategy</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Risk assessment</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does IRAP Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-green-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Phase</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Timeline</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Notes</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">ITA Contact & Assessment</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-4 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Initial eligibility review</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Project Development</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-6 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">With ITA guidance</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">NRC Review</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">4-8 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Technical evaluation</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Agreement Signing</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">1-2 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Contribution agreement</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold\">Total Process</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold\">2-4 months</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">From initial contact</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Timeline can vary significantly based on project\n                  complexity and regional demand. Engage early—IRAP fiscal year-end (March 31)\n                  often sees faster processing to deploy remaining budgets.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Common Mistakes Get IRAP Applications Rejected?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Weak Technical Innovation</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          IRAP requires genuine technological uncertainty. Incremental\n                          improvements or routine engineering don't qualify. You must\n                          demonstrate that you're solving a problem for which no\n                          known solution exists.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">No Clear Commercialization Path</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          IRAP funds innovation that will generate economic returns.\n                          You need to demonstrate market demand, customer validation,\n                          and a realistic go-to-market strategy.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Insufficient Technical Team</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          IRAP evaluates your capacity to execute. Projects without\n                          qualified technical personnel or relevant R&D experience\n                          are rejected regardless of the technology's potential.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">4</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Applying After Project Starts</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          IRAP cannot fund retroactive costs. Contact your ITA before\n                          starting the project—costs incurred before approval are\n                          ineligible.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">IRAP vs SR&ED: Which is Better?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-green-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Factor</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">IRAP</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">SR&ED</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Timing</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">Upfront funding</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">After expenditure (tax filing)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Application</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Before project starts</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">After fiscal year-end</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Amount</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Up to $1M (67% of costs)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">35% refundable (CCPCs)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Stacking</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">Can combine with SR&ED</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Can combine with IRAP</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Best For</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Cash flow sensitive SMEs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Established R&D operations</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Best Strategy:</strong> Apply for both! IRAP and SR&ED can be\n                  combined—IRAP funding reduces SR&ED eligible expenses, but you still\n                  get credits on the remaining costs. Many companies maximize returns by\n                  leveraging both programs.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Alternative Programs for R&D Funding</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SR&ED Tax Credits</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Tax credits for R&D expenditures—35% refundable for CCPCs,\n                    15% non-refundable for others.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sred-tax-credits-2026\">\n                    SR&ED Guide →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Strategic Innovation Fund</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Large-scale R&D projects ($10M+) with significant economic\n                    impact potential.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/strategic-innovation-fund-canada-guide\">\n                    SIF Guide →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Regional Development Agencies</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    ACOA, WD, FedDev Ontario, and others provide regional innovation\n                    funding.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/canada-regional-economic-development-grants-guide\">\n                    Regional Grants →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Provincial R&D Programs</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Many provinces offer additional R&D funding that stacks with\n                    federal programs like IRAP.\n                  </p>\n                  <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2\">\n                    <a href=\"/blog/ontario-government-business-grants\">Ontario →</a>\n                    <a href=\"/blog/bc-business-grants-2026\">BC →</a>\n                    <a href=\"/blog/alberta-business-grants-2026\">Alberta →</a>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                {faqData.map((faq, index) => (\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg flex items-start\">\n                        {faq.question}\n                      </h3>\n                      <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-2 ml-7\">{faq.answer}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
